title: METALLICA - LIVE IN GLOBEN STOCKHOLM 4TH OF MAY 2009
description:

Total Running Time: 2:05:20

SHOW NOTES

*This was a makeup show for the canceled gig on March 8, 2009 after James as taken down by a mighty oyster.

*This was the 12th time that Metallica performed in Stockholm.

*This was the first time that Holier Than Thou was performed in Stockholm.

*This was the first time in 13 years that Motorbreath was performed in Stockholm.  It was last played here on November 15, 1996.

*This was the first time in 16 years that Welcome Home (Sanitarium) was performed in Stockholm.  It was last played here on May 30, 1993.
